            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. Constat me <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Dominicus"
                                >Dominicus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/80">sancte <placeName ref="#places/7"
                                >Bononiensis</placeName> Ecclesie</orgName> prepositus <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monast(erii)</rs>
                        <rs key="#Hospitals">exenedochio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Fundi #Petiae #Hay/fodder #Monasteries #Hospitals">Sancti
                            Donati</orgName> accepi a te <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Leo"
                                >Leo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> itemque sancte Bononiensis Ecclesie
                        filius quondam <persName><name ref="Leo/Petronge">Leoni
                            Petrogne</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Rent_in_money">pensio</rs> pro rebus illis in <rs key="#Fundi"
                            >fundo</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Fundi"><placeName key="#Fundi"
                            >Salecto</placeName></geogName> et pro <rs key="#Petiae #Hay/fodder"
                            >petja una terra que est prato</rs> in loco qui ditjtur <geogName
                            key="#Petiae #Hay/fodder"><placeName key="#Petiae #Hay/fodder"
                                >Pulia</placeName></geogName>, quas per <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">enfiteosin</rs> tenetis ad iura
                        suprascriptis mon(asterii), pro omnia sicut in ipsa enfiteosin legitur in
                            <rs key="#Rent_in_money">argento denario uno et medietatem de alio
                            denario</rs> pro trasactis ind(ici)onibus undecima, duodecima et per
                        pres(ente) tertjadecima, per unaquaque ind(icione) <rs key="#Rent_in_money"
                            >denario medio</rs>. Unde pro m(unimine) vestro feci vobis h(oc)
                        d(eaccepto) m(ense) mar(cio), ind(icione) suprascripta tertjadecima. Scripto
                        per m(anum) <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Ursus">Ursi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">not(arii)</rs>.</ab>
                </div>
